{
  "texts": [
    "Regarding the third level of remembering the session and acting on this information, ChatGPT's ability to recall previous interactions enhances the learning process by fostering continuity in the learning experience-a principle implicitly supported by the Zone of Proximal Development (ZPD).",
    "By remembering past questions and answers, each interaction contributes to a coherent and cumulative learning journey, gradually guiding the learner from dependence to independence.",
    "However, this functionality is limited by the current capabilities of Chat-GPT technologies to maintain and utilize a long-term memory of the learner.",
    "The 4 th level of diagnosing and helping with areas of weaknesses, is a direct application of the ZPD, where the aim is to identify the learner's current level of understanding (actual development level) and their potential development level (with assistance).",
    "By diagnosing areas of weakness, ChatGPT can effectively scaffold the learning process, providing targeted help to address knowledge gaps and strengthen areas of weakness."
  ]
}